cz.kinst.jakub.coursemanager.utils

Class TabbedActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • cz.kinst.jakub.coursemanager.utils.TabbedActivity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CMActivity

    public class TabbedActivity
extends Activity
    Base Android Activity class providing Tab functionality. Activity Content is divided into several Tabs, which are represented by a button with label. When user clicks on the button, tab is immediatelly switched as well as content.
    Author:
    Jakub Kinst
